Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.22,0:31:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有色情的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.77,0:31:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.14,0:31:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.27,0:31:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.61,0:31:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,, -好難為情 -難為情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.34,0:31:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想看啊 不可以遮住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.28,0:31:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能看這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.72,0:31:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,想你看過來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.06,0:31:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,別害羞看這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.33,0:31:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的看著的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.23,0:31:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.07,0:31:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡被看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.75,0:32:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,用那個自慰看看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.53,0:32:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,下流的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.38,0:32:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,, -這樣子嗎 -倒下去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.97,0:33:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有下流的氣味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.29,0:33:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡有的濕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.83,0:33:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.24,0:33:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.72,0:33:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,下流的形狀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.02,0:33:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好色情
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.70,0:34:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,直接的比較舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.25,0:34:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.25,0:35:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再靠近點看小穴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.89,0:35:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.47,0:35:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把屁股翹起來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.04,0:35:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,流了好多汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.56,0:36:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.30,0:36:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,濕了很多呢果然
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.00,0:36:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,, -怎麼回事 -濕了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.11,0:36:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有濕痕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.07,0:36:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,把膝蓋併攏
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.90,0:37:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出來好屁股呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.57,0:37:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害呢 再伸出來點看看
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.49,0:37:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,都陷進小穴里了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.81,0:37:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.93,0:37:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,, -緊身褲被撕破了 -沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.77,0:38:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可以看看嗎不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.41,0:39:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,在做色情的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.16,0:40:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.09,0:40:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面也喜歡嗎
