Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.76,0:41:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.68,0:41:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一抖一抖的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.71,0:41:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.05,0:41:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.62,0:41:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真色情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.56,0:41:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很色情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.53,0:41:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想了色情的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.90,0:41:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.92,0:42:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是色情的形狀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.76,0:42:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,色情的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.75,0:42:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.46,0:42:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.46,0:43:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼的濕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.83,0:43:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,濕灑灑的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.33,0:44:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,又高潮了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.52,0:45:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,張開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.96,0:45:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股這樣子對
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.97,0:45:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,色情的姿勢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.00,0:45:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,屁眼子也看見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.88,0:46:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,全看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.25,0:46:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,難為情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.88,0:47:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.81,0:47:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.21,0:47:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.70,0:48:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,起來一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.56,0:48:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,脫掉比較好
