Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.64,0:48:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼硬了 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.71,0:48:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.38,0:48:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,, -說不出□嗎 -好難為情
