Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.32,0:49:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看著我眼睛說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.57,0:49:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.77,0:49:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.11,0:49:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,, -說了 -沒說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.44,0:49:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.25,0:49:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,, -肉棒 -肉棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.62,0:49:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒看著我眼睛說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.70,0:49:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,, -說了 -沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.27,0:49:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,, -沒說哦 -說了2次
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.91,0:49:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,, -沒看著我眼睛說 -肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.14,0:49:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那你來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.88,0:49:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.96,0:50:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.04,0:50:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.60,0:50:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,, -變大了 -摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.11,0:50:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,變大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.55,0:50:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,變成這樣是因為誰
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.22,0:50:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,, -誰啊 -不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.06,0:50:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好好說名字是因為誰
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.09,0:50:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,, -我 -說名字
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.60,0:50:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.27,0:50:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,說下自己的名字
