Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.12,0:52:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,, -進不去 -盡量往裡伸
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.93,0:52:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,進去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.34,0:53:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就用嘴含著看看
