Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.99,1:22:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真色情
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.22,1:22:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.73,1:22:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,臉上有好多精液
