Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.65,1:22:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,, -好濃呢 -濃啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.26,1:22:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很合適嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.59,1:22:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼擦擦吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.23,1:23:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,沒被這樣射過吧
